sequenceDiagram
    participant D as Voce
    participant A as Agent Mode
    participant P as Projeto DevFlow

    D->>A: Prompt com descricao do CRUD
    A->>P: #read copilot-instructions.md
    A->>P: #read package.json
    A->>P: #read index.js
    A-->>A: #todos Planejar passos
    A->>P: #edit Criar routes/projects.js
    A->>P: #edit Atualizar index.js com nova rota
    A->>P: #execute npm start
    A->>P: #execute curl para testar POST
    A->>P: #execute curl para testar GET
    A->>P: #execute curl para testar DELETE
    A-->>D: Mostra diff de todas as alteracoes
    D-->>A: Apply (aceitar alteracoes)